AI logo generator FAQs

How does the AI logo design generator work?

The Wix AI logo generator is an online design tool powered by Artificial Intelligence (AI) that allows you to chat with AI, create and customize a professional logo for free.

How to create a logo in Wix using AI?

Chat with the AI and answer a few simple questions about your brand identity, tagline and vibe you’re going for. Then sit back as the Wix AI logo creator generates unique logos for you to choose from. Once you’ve chosen your favorite, you can easily edit the theme, text, colors and icons any way you want.

How long will it take to generate a logo for my business using AI?

Once you’ve answered a few questions in the AI chat, the AI logo creator will generate a logo for you in a few seconds. The amount of editing you want to do until you’re happy with your logo is totally up to you but should only take a few minutes.

What types of files do I get with my purchased logo?

When you create a logo with AI using Wix, you get all the types of files that you need for your business, unlike with other logo software platforms. You'll receive different logo formats depending on the package you choose. All of the packages include the high-resolution PNG files (5000 x 5000 px) in your original logo colors as well as black, white and transparent color variations. These files are ideal for using online. If you're planning on printing your logo from the logo creator, we recommend purchasing one of the packages that include high quality SVG vector files.

Can I create a logo using AI for free?

You can create a logo with AI for free when you use Wix’s free AI logo maker. If you need high-resolution files, you can purchase and download your logo from the AI logo maker at any time.

Can I edit my logo after purchasing/downloading it?

In short, yes, you can, though it depends on your plan. With some of our plans, you have the option to edit your logo after downloading it. For unlimited customization, we recommend choosing the 'Brand Plus' plan (logo-only) or the 'Business' and 'Unlimited' plans (logo + online presence). These plans give you the freedom to make updates to your logo’s design even after downloading the logo files.

Do I own my logo after downloading it?

You get full commercial usage rights to your logo after choosing a package that allows you to buy and download it. You’ll be able to use your royalty-free logo wherever and whenever you like.

Is an AI logo design suitable for all types of businesses?

In short, yes. When you use AI for logo design, you can generate logos that are suitable for all types of businesses. Whether you're a startup, small business or large enterprise, AI can generate unique, professional logos tailored to your specific brand's needs and industry.

Can I customize the generated logo designs?

Once you’ve used the AI logo generator free of charge, you can choose your favorite design and customize it however you want. You can use the intuitive editor to tweak everything including the color theme, typography, text, icons, layout and more until you’re happy with the design.
